nodes.text: Vine swinging was a sport practiced by the Ewoks, a species of diminutive humanoids living on the Forest Moon of Endor. On the occasion of the Ewok midsummer festival, a vine swinging contest was held, among several other sporting events. Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka, the princess of the Bright Tree Village, once entered such a vine swinging competition. When she lost hold of the vine, Kneesaa accidentally landed on a tree log and ended up winning the Log Ride Contest.
